## Environment and build

- Build tool: Vite with React plugin in [vite.config.js](mdc:vite.config.js).
- Commands: `npm run dev`, `npm run build`, `npm run preview`.

## Vite env variables (required)

Define the following in a `.env` file at project root (Vite reads `VITE_*`):

```
VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=...
VITE_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=...
VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=...
VITE_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=...
VITE_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=...
VITE_FIREBASE_APP_ID=...
VITE_FIREBASE_MEASUREMENT_ID=...
```

Restart dev server after changes. All Firebase initialization reads from these keys in [src/config/firebase.jsx](mdc:src/config/firebase.jsx).

## Assets

- Place static images under `src/assets/img` and audio under `src/assets/sounds`. Vite will bundle and hash as needed.
